short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extension for Chrome that display the additional fees you have to pay when you order from Thomann (Germany) to Macedonia.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extension for Chrome that display additional fees and the total amount you have to pay when you order from Thomann (Germany) to Macedonia.
